A Place In The Sun presenter Jasmine Harman, 46, has shared a fun clip of herself jumping into a pool in a blue bikini as she films in Crete.Jasmine looked stunning in the two-piece as she dived into the water with a huge smile on her face.In view of her 106,00 followers she wrote: “My favourite way to end a long, hot day filming.“Apart from the bit where the water went up my nose.”Jasmine then added a poll which asked her followers: “Anyone else learning to love their wobbly bits?”